              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/29361778/" class="">第219页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Shoon/" class=" " title="何羊">何羊</a>
                (夜如何其？)
              
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="29361778">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">君子之德，有张有弛，故不常矜庄，而时戏谑。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-11-15 14:59</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>君子之德，有张有弛，故不常矜庄，而时戏谑。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







<div class="rec-sec">

    <span class="rec">

